    "url": "",
    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe AI Video Content Creator & Social Media Intern will support the marketing team by creating short-form and long-form video content for social channels across APJ. The role is suited for someone who understands technology storytelling, social-native editing, and the fast-moving content style of AI and cloud infrastructure audiences.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Research trending AI, cloud, GPU, and developer topics and turn them into video concepts.\n- Plan short-form videos, product explainers, event recaps, interview clips, and social media assets.\n- Edit videos with tools such as Premiere Pro, After Effects, Final Cut Pro, CapCut, or similar.\n- Add subtitles, motion graphics, transitions, sound cues, and visual hooks to improve watch time.\n- Support daily social channel operations, including posting, titles, tags, descriptions, and thumbnail/cover design.\n- Track performance metrics such as views, watch time, saves, shares, and engagement, then suggest content improvements.\n- Work with marketing, product, and technical teams to translate complex AI infrastructure concepts into content that is easy to understand.\n\nRequirements\n- Current student or early-career candidate in media, communications, design, marketing, computer science, or a related field.\n- Strong sense of social video pacing, hooks, captions, thumbnails, and platform-specific formats.\n- Hands-on editing experience with at least one mainstream video tool.\n- Ability to work independently in a remote APJ environment and deliver on schedule.\n- Interest in AI, cloud computing, GPU infrastructure, developer tools, or enterprise technology.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience operating Xiaohongshu, WeChat, LinkedIn, YouTube Shorts, TikTok, or similar channels.\n- Basic design skills for covers, motion cards, and simple product visuals.\n- Bilingual English/Mandarin communication ability.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\nAI 视频内容与社媒实习生将支持市场团队，为 APJ 区域的社媒渠道制作短视频、长视频和品牌内容。这个岗位适合熟悉科技内容表达、懂社媒节奏、愿意把 AI / 云计算 / GPU 基础设施这类复杂主题讲得更清楚的人。\n\n岗位职责\n- 调研 AI、云计算、GPU、开发者工具等热门话题，并转化为视频选题。\n- 策划短视频、产品解释视频、活动回顾、采访切片和社媒素材。\n- 使用 Premiere Pro、After Effects、Final Cut Pro、剪映或类似工具完成视频剪辑。\n- 添加字幕、动效、转场、音效和开头 hook，提升完播率和观看体验。\n- 支持账号日常运营，包括发布、标题、标签、描述、封面和内容排期。\n- 跟踪播放量、完播率、收藏、转发、互动等数据，并提出内容优化建议。\n- 与市场、产品和技术团队协作，将复杂的 AI 基础设施概念转化为更易理解的内容。\n\n任职要求\n- 在校生或早期职业候选人，传媒、传播、设计、市场、计算机或相关专业优先。\n- 理解社媒视频节奏、开头钩子、字幕、封面和不同平台的内容风格。\n- 至少熟练掌握一种主流视频剪辑工具。\n- 能适应远程协作，按时交付内容。\n- 对 AI、云计算、GPU 基础设施、开发者工具或企业科技内容感兴趣。\n\n加分项\n- 运营过小红书、微信公众号、LinkedIn、YouTube Shorts、TikTok 等渠道。\n- 具备基础设计能力，可制作封面、动效卡片和简单产品视觉。\n- 具备中英文沟通能力。",
