    "url": "",
    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe UX/UI Designer will design product experiences for AI cloud and infrastructure workflows. The role requires turning highly technical user journeys into clear, usable, and scalable interfaces for developers, operators, and enterprise customers.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Design end-to-end user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity interfaces for AI infrastructure products.\n- Translate complex workflows such as GPU resource management, cluster operations, inference services, billing, monitoring, and access control into intuitive product experiences.\n- Partner with product managers, engineers, and go-to-market teams to define user requirements and design priorities.\n- Build and maintain reusable design components, interaction patterns, and visual standards.\n- Conduct user research, feedback review, usability checks, and iteration based on real customer workflows.\n- Create clear design specs and collaborate closely with engineering during implementation.\n\nRequirements\n- Experience designing B2B SaaS, developer tools, cloud platforms, infrastructure products, or technical dashboards.\n- Strong portfolio showing product thinking, information architecture, interaction design, and visual execution.\n- Ability to simplify complex technical systems without losing accuracy.\n- Familiarity with Figma and modern design collaboration workflows.\n- Good communication skills and ability to work with engineering-heavy teams.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience with AI, cloud computing, Kubernetes, observability, billing, or data platform products.\n- Experience building or maintaining design systems.\n- Ability to create lightweight motion, illustrations, or product marketing visuals.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\nUX/UI 设计师将负责 AI 云和基础设施产品的用户体验与界面设计，把复杂的技术流程转化为清晰、可用、可扩展的产品体验。主要用户包括开发者、运维团队和企业客户。\n\n岗位职责\n- 设计 AI 基础设施产品的端到端用户流程、线框图、原型和高保真界面。\n- 将 GPU 资源管理、集群运维、推理服务、账单、监控、权限管理等复杂流程转化为直观产品体验。\n- 与产品经理、工程师和商业化团队协作，梳理用户需求和设计优先级。\n- 建设和维护可复用的设计组件、交互模式和视觉规范。\n- 基于真实客户工作流进行用户研究、反馈整理、可用性检查和迭代。\n- 输出清晰设计规范，并与工程团队协作推进落地。\n\n任职要求\n- 有 B2B SaaS、开发者工具、云平台、基础设施产品或技术型 Dashboard 设计经验。\n- 作品集能体现产品思维、信息架构、交互设计和视觉执行能力。\n- 能把复杂技术系统讲清楚、设计清楚，同时保持准确性。\n- 熟练使用 Figma 和现代设计协作流程。\n- 沟通能力强，能与工程密集型团队高效协作。\n\n加分项\n- 有 AI、云计算、Kubernetes、可观测性、账单或数据平台产品经验。\n- 有设计系统建设或维护经验。\n- 能制作轻量动效、插画或产品营销视觉。",
