    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe Senior Product Manager, AI Platform owns product strategy and execution for AI platform capabilities. This role translates customer infrastructure needs into platform products that support scalable training, inference, deployment, monitoring, and resource management workflows.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Define product strategy, roadmap, and success metrics for AI platform capabilities.\n- Own customer-facing workflows for GPU resources, model deployment, inference services, monitoring, billing, access control, and developer experience.\n- Work closely with engineering to scope requirements, prioritize tradeoffs, and ship reliable platform features.\n- Partner with sales, solutions, customer success, and infrastructure teams to understand customer needs and product gaps.\n- Analyze usage data, customer feedback, competitive products, and infrastructure constraints to guide roadmap decisions.\n- Write product requirements, launch plans, internal enablement materials, and customer-facing documentation.\n\nRequirements\n- Product management experience in cloud platforms, AI platforms, developer tools, infrastructure, MLOps, or enterprise SaaS.\n- Strong technical fluency and ability to work directly with engineering teams on complex systems.\n- Clear product judgment around user workflows, prioritization, reliability, and business impact.\n- Ability to communicate with both technical and non-technical stakeholders.\n- Ownership mindset in a fast-moving, high-ambiguity environment.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience with GPU infrastructure, Kubernetes, model serving, inference APIs, observability, or AI developer platforms.\n- Experience launching 0-to-1 products or scaling early platform capabilities.\n- Prior work with enterprise AI customers or developer-facing products.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\n高级产品经理，AI 平台方向，负责 AI 平台能力的产品策略与落地，将客户在基础设施层面的需求转化为可规模化的平台产品，覆盖训练、推理、部署、监控、资源管理等核心工作流。\n\n岗位职责\n- 定义 AI 平台能力的产品策略、路线图和成功指标。\n- 负责 GPU 资源、模型部署、推理服务、监控、账单、权限管理和开发者体验等面向客户的核心流程。\n- 与工程团队紧密协作，拆解需求、明确优先级、平衡技术取舍并推动功能上线。\n- 与销售、解决方案、客户成功和基础设施团队合作，理解客户需求和产品缺口。\n- 结合使用数据、客户反馈、竞品分析和基础设施约束，推动路线图决策。\n- 编写 PRD、发布计划、内部 enablement 材料和客户文档。\n\n任职要求\n- 有云平台、AI 平台、开发者工具、基础设施、MLOps 或企业 SaaS 产品经验。\n- 具备较强技术理解力，能和工程团队围绕复杂系统直接协作。\n- 对用户流程、优先级、可靠性和业务影响有清晰产品判断。\n- 能同时与技术和非技术团队沟通。\n- 在高速变化和高不确定性环境中具备 owner 意识。\n\n加分项\n- 有 GPU 基础设施、Kubernetes、模型服务、推理 API、可观测性或 AI 开发者平台经验。\n- 有 0 到 1 产品发布或早期平台能力规模化经验。\n- 有企业 AI 客户或开发者产品经验。",
