    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe IT Operation Specialist supports day-to-day IT operations for a fast-growing AI infrastructure team. The role covers office IT, device setup, troubleshooting, access coordination, internal systems, and reliable technical support for employees.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Provide daily IT support for employees, including laptops, peripherals, conferencing equipment, network access, and office devices.\n- Handle onboarding and offboarding IT workflows, including device preparation, account setup, permission changes, and asset recovery.\n- Troubleshoot hardware, software, network, VPN, printer, and collaboration tool issues.\n- Maintain IT inventory, asset records, access lists, and operational documentation.\n- Coordinate with vendors and internal teams for procurement, repairs, replacements, and office technology improvements.\n- Support security and compliance practices such as access control, device management, and basic endpoint hygiene.\n\nRequirements\n- Experience in IT support, helpdesk, office IT, system administration, or technical operations.\n- Familiarity with macOS/Windows devices, common SaaS tools, identity/access workflows, and networking basics.\n- Strong service mindset, documentation discipline, and troubleshooting ability.\n- Ability to support users onsite and communicate clearly with both technical and non-technical colleagues.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience in startup, cloud, AI, or hardware-heavy environments.\n- Familiarity with MDM, IAM, Slack, Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, VPN, and endpoint security tools.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\nIT 运维专员负责支持快速增长的 AI 基础设施团队日常 IT 运维，覆盖办公室 IT、设备配置、故障排查、权限协同、内部系统和员工技术支持。\n\n岗位职责\n- 为员工提供日常 IT 支持，包括电脑、外设、会议设备、网络接入和办公室设备。\n- 处理入职和离职 IT 流程，包括设备准备、账号开通、权限变更和资产回收。\n- 排查硬件、软件、网络、VPN、打印机和协作工具问题。\n- 维护 IT 库存、资产记录、权限清单和运维文档。\n- 对接供应商和内部团队，支持采购、维修、更换和办公室技术体验优化。\n- 支持访问控制、设备管理和基础终端安全等安全合规实践。\n\n任职要求\n- 有 IT 支持、Helpdesk、办公室 IT、系统管理或技术运维经验。\n- 熟悉 macOS/Windows 设备、常见 SaaS 工具、身份权限流程和基础网络知识。\n- 服务意识强，文档习惯好，具备清晰的问题排查能力。\n- 能支持现场用户，并与技术和非技术同事清晰沟通。\n\n加分项\n- 有初创公司、云计算、AI 或硬件密集型环境经验。\n- 熟悉 MDM、IAM、Slack、Google Workspace、Microsoft 365、VPN 和终端安全工具。",
