    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe GPU Resource Acquisition Manager sources and secures GPU capacity and infrastructure resources to support global AI cloud growth. This role sits at the intersection of infrastructure sourcing, vendor partnerships, capacity planning, and commercial execution.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Identify and evaluate GPU capacity, data center, hosting, hardware, and infrastructure resource opportunities.\n- Build relationships with vendors, suppliers, data center partners, hardware providers, and strategic infrastructure partners.\n- Support capacity planning for GPU cloud growth across regions, including availability, cost, lead time, and deployment feasibility.\n- Coordinate commercial terms, procurement workflows, delivery schedules, and internal approval processes.\n- Work with infrastructure, finance, legal, and operations teams to move resource opportunities from evaluation to execution.\n- Track market supply, GPU availability, pricing trends, and partner landscape changes.\n\nRequirements\n- Experience in infrastructure sourcing, procurement, vendor management, data center partnerships, cloud capacity, hardware supply chain, or related commercial roles.\n- Understanding of GPU, server, data center, cloud infrastructure, or AI compute capacity markets.\n- Strong negotiation, relationship management, analytical, and execution skills.\n- Ability to coordinate across technical and business stakeholders.\n\nNice to Have\n- Existing network in GPU suppliers, data center providers, colocation providers, hardware vendors, or cloud infrastructure partners.\n- Experience with capacity reservation, large hardware procurement, or multi-region infrastructure planning.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\nGPU 资源拓展经理负责拓展和获取 GPU 算力及基础设施资源，支持全球 AI 云业务增长。该岗位处于基础设施资源拓展、供应商合作、容量规划和商业执行的交叉点。\n\n岗位职责\n- 识别和评估 GPU 算力、数据中心、托管、硬件和基础设施资源机会。\n- 建立并维护供应商、数据中心合作伙伴、硬件厂商和战略基础设施伙伴关系。\n- 支持跨区域 GPU 云容量规划，评估资源可用性、成本、交付周期和部署可行性。\n- 协调商业条款、采购流程、交付计划和内部审批。\n- 与基础设施、财务、法务和运营团队合作，将资源机会从评估推进到执行。\n- 跟踪市场供给、GPU 可用性、价格趋势和合作伙伴格局变化。\n\n任职要求\n- 有基础设施资源拓展、采购、供应商管理、数据中心合作、云容量、硬件供应链或相关商业岗位经验。\n- 理解 GPU、服务器、数据中心、云基础设施或 AI 算力容量市场。\n- 具备较强谈判、关系管理、分析和落地执行能力。\n- 能协调技术和商业团队共同推进项目。\n\n加分项\n- 在 GPU 供应商、数据中心、托管服务商、硬件厂商或云基础设施伙伴中有资源网络。\n- 有容量预留、大规模硬件采购或多区域基础设施规划经验。",
