    "url": "",
    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe Logistics Manager owns logistics execution for infrastructure and hardware-related workflows. This role ensures that equipment, components, shipments, documents, and vendor coordination move reliably across teams and locations.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Manage logistics operations for hardware, infrastructure equipment, office assets, and related shipments.\n- Coordinate with vendors, freight forwarders, warehouses, customs brokers, internal operations, and finance teams.\n- Track shipment timelines, documentation, delivery status, exceptions, and issue resolution.\n- Maintain accurate logistics records, purchase/shipping documents, asset information, and process documentation.\n- Support import/export coordination, customs documents, inventory handoff, and receiving workflows.\n- Identify process bottlenecks and improve logistics reliability, cost control, and communication cadence.\n\nRequirements\n- Experience in logistics, supply chain, hardware operations, import/export coordination, or vendor operations.\n- Strong attention to detail, ownership, follow-through, and documentation discipline.\n- Ability to coordinate multiple stakeholders and resolve time-sensitive operational issues.\n- Familiarity with shipment tracking, vendor communication, and basic finance/procurement workflows.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience with data center equipment, servers, networking hardware, GPU/IT hardware, or cross-border logistics.\n- Bilingual English/Mandarin communication ability.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\n物流经理负责基础设施和硬件相关流程中的物流执行，确保设备、组件、货运、文档和供应商协同能够在团队和地点之间稳定推进。\n\n岗位职责\n- 管理硬件、基础设施设备、办公室资产及相关货运的物流运营。\n- 协调供应商、货代、仓储、报关、内部运营和财务团队。\n- 跟踪运输时间、文档、交付状态、异常情况和问题解决。\n- 维护准确的物流记录、采购/运输文档、资产信息和流程文档。\n- 支持进出口协调、报关文件、库存交接和收货流程。\n- 识别流程瓶颈，提升物流可靠性、成本控制和沟通节奏。\n\n任职要求\n- 有物流、供应链、硬件运营、进出口协调或供应商运营经验。\n- 细致可靠，owner 意识强，执行闭环和文档习惯好。\n- 能协调多方并处理时间敏感型运营问题。\n- 熟悉货运跟踪、供应商沟通和基础财务/采购流程。\n\n加分项\n- 有数据中心设备、服务器、网络硬件、GPU/IT 硬件或跨境物流经验。\n- 具备中英文沟通能力。",
