    "url": "",
    "jdEn": "Role Overview\n\nThe Developer Advocate / Tech Evangelist helps developers, AI builders, and technical customers understand and adopt AI infrastructure products. The role combines technical storytelling, demos, documentation, community engagement, and feedback collection.\n\nResponsibilities\n- Create technical content such as tutorials, demos, explainers, blog posts, videos, sample projects, and talks.\n- Translate complex AI infrastructure topics into practical guidance for developers and technical decision makers.\n- Build demos around model deployment, inference, GPU usage, APIs, developer workflows, and platform capabilities.\n- Engage with developer communities, customers, events, and online channels to increase product awareness and adoption.\n- Work with product, engineering, marketing, and solutions teams to identify developer pain points and content opportunities.\n- Collect community and customer feedback and route insights back to product teams.\n\nRequirements\n- Technical background in software engineering, developer relations, solutions engineering, ML engineering, or technical content.\n- Ability to explain complex systems clearly through writing, speaking, demos, and visuals.\n- Hands-on familiarity with Python, APIs, cloud platforms, model serving, or AI developer workflows.\n- Strong communication skills and comfort engaging with technical audiences.\n\nNice to Have\n- Experience with LLM inference, GPU infrastructure, Kubernetes, vLLM, SGLang, Ray, or MLOps.\n- Existing developer community presence or portfolio of technical content.\n- Bilingual English/Mandarin content or presentation ability.",
    "jdZh": "岗位介绍\n\n开发者布道师 / 技术传播岗位面向开发者、AI builders 和技术客户，帮助他们理解并采用 AI 基础设施产品。该岗位结合技术表达、Demo、文档、社区互动和用户反馈收集。\n\n岗位职责\n- 创作技术内容，包括教程、Demo、解释型文章、博客、视频、示例项目和技术演讲。\n- 将复杂的 AI 基础设施主题转化为开发者和技术决策者能直接使用的实践指南。\n- 围绕模型部署、推理、GPU 使用、API、开发者工作流和平台能力构建 Demo。\n- 参与开发者社区、客户沟通、活动和线上渠道，提高产品认知和采用。\n- 与产品、工程、市场和解决方案团队合作，识别开发者痛点和内容机会。\n- 收集社区和客户反馈，并将洞察传递给产品团队。\n\n任职要求\n- 具备软件工程、开发者关系、解决方案工程、机器学习工程或技术内容背景。\n- 能通过写作、演讲、Demo 和视觉表达清晰解释复杂系统。\n- 熟悉 Python、API、云平台、模型服务或 AI 开发者工作流。\n- 沟通能力强，能与技术受众自然互动。\n\n加分项\n- 熟悉 LLM 推理、GPU 基础设施、Kubernetes、vLLM、SGLang、Ray 或 MLOps。\n- 有开发者社区影响力或技术内容作品集。\n- 具备中英文内容创作或演讲能力。",
